## Palantir Technologies’ 3-year revenue CAGR

Using the latest three-year period available as of April 7, 2025—FY2021 through FY2024:

- **FY2021 revenue:** $1.541889 billion
- **FY2024 revenue:** $2.865507 billion
- **Number of annual periods:** 3

\[
\text{Revenue CAGR}=\left(\frac{2.865507}{1.541889}\right)^{1/3}-1
\]

\[
\text{Revenue CAGR}=0.229465\approx \boxed{22.95\%}
\]

**Answer: Palantir Technologies’ revenue CAGR from FY2021 to FY2024 was approximately 22.95% per year.**

